{"type": "article", "id": 14729, "title": "日本这家昏暗的寿司店，想给你私人化的用餐体验", "description": "说实话，感觉这样吃饭压力很大", "date": "2015-09-10T11:35:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 15852, "name": "寿司店"}, {"id": 3000, "name": "店铺设计"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 107, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021100352ZJXuixV6MrvUeHf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.sushiyoshii.com\" target=\"_blank\">Sushi Yoshii</a> 是今年 6 月份在日本新开的一家寿司店，店铺面积极小，只接受提前电话定位，店主通过空间设计，想打造一个私人化的用餐体验。<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2015/09/09/sushi-yoshii-tokyo/\" target=\"_blank\">店铺装修沿用了日本哲学中常见的沉寂和单一，</a>人、寿司、空间相结合，或许能打造出特殊的用餐体验。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110030VFTqckJQpaIRj1Ps.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"483\" title=\"狭小的空间\" alt=\"狭小的空间\" data-ratio=\"0.7546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>狭小的空间</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110031ojUY6BLIiwOX2mvn.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"483\" title=\"空间稍显昏暗\" alt=\"空间稍显昏暗\" data-ratio=\"0.7546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>空间稍显昏暗</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110031Rno0sHgbQLY4cE53.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"483\" title=\"从远望去\" alt=\"从远望去\" data-ratio=\"0.7546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>从远望去</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110031z5xLtIQWqyEsMw9n.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"483\" title=\"全景\" alt=\"全景\" data-ratio=\"0.7546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>全景</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这家店铺是由设计事务所 <a href=\"http://www.suppose.jp/\">Suppose\r\nDesign Office</a> 设计完成的，餐厅里质朴的木质家具也是由他们挑选。如果不稍加留意，食客们很容易忽略掉墙上悬挂的艺术家作品，这些作品来自 Hiroshi Sugimoto, Franz West 和 Yayoi Kusama.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110032c9vYMTVemzKRowNi.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"483\" title=\"操作台\" alt=\"操作台\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.7546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span style=\"text-align:center;\">操作台及艺术品，这幅艺术品来自 </span><span style=\"text-align:center;\">Hiroshi Sugimoto</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021100324nb7vZDzXmJqIBGQ.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"355\" title=\"寿司店网站上的营业时间和地址\" alt=\"寿司店网站上的营业时间和地址\" data-ratio=\"0.5546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>寿司店网站上的营业时间和地址</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110033lFwOU9Zm3fTAXpJ2.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"337\" title=\"图片来自寿司店网站\" alt=\"图片来自寿司店网站\" data-ratio=\"0.5265625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>图片来自寿司店网站</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t除了这家寿司店， Suppose Design Office 还完成了许多建筑的设计，下面是他们完成的几个案例：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110033lVO47dK9wuyFJtx0.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"483\" title=\"宇都宮の家\" alt=\"宇都宮の家\" data-ratio=\"0.7546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>宇都宮の家</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021100338bIHKQz7BA9RlnxZ.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"483\" title=\"宇都宮の家\" alt=\"宇都宮の家\" data-ratio=\"0.7546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>宇都宮の家</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110034wPv9tG3Zi8NVUCOz.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"483\" title=\"海老名の家\" alt=\"海老名の家\" data-ratio=\"0.7546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>海老名の家</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110034MTWm4iJNF1oC9UPb.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"483\" title=\"NI Project 概念图\" alt=\"NI Project 概念图\" data-ratio=\"0.7546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>NI Project 概念图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110035KJVARp3C5f0awd1z.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"483\" title=\"NI Project 概念图\" alt=\"NI Project 概念图\" data-ratio=\"0.7546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>NI Project 概念图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2015/09/09/sushi-yoshii-tokyo/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>spoon-tamago</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}